trans-unit.source: Provides an object model that allows you to construct activities dynamically that interface with the WF designer and runtime using <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ICustomTypeDescriptor"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller en objektmodell som gör det möjligt att konstruera aktiviteter dynamiskt gränssnittet med WF-designer och runtime med <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ICustomTypeDescriptor"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.DynamicActivity"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Activities.DynamicActivity"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: With <xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity> you can create new activities without creating new types.
trans-unit.target: Med <xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity>kan du skapa nya aktiviteter utan att skapa nya typer.</xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity> with its associated XAML support in <xref:System.Activities.XamlIntegration.ActivityXamlServices> allows new arguments to be defined in XAML and bound by the host without requiring XAML to be compiled.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity>med dess associerade XAML-stöd i <xref:System.Activities.XamlIntegration.ActivityXamlServices>tillåter nya argument kan definieras i XAML och bundna av värden utan XAML sammanställas.</xref:System.Activities.XamlIntegration.ActivityXamlServices></xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity>
